Daredevil is the best new show to grace our TV screens in the last couple of years. Whether you are a comic book fan or not, you will enjoy the passionate, heartfelt drama and exciting action. It's intense and gritty but there a moments of poetry and insight in the script. There are characters that you will fall in love with. Marvel studios have worked a miracle adapting this dark, vigilante hero to TV. The setting, the streets of New York city is like another character. While Thor and co are off saving the world or the galaxy, Daredevil is stopping the thugs and low lives from hurting you and me. It has a real sense of place in the Marvel universe.